                <div class="jonra" data-uuid="cd8f36e57c6b4990bdd6c3a0e8fa81c0">
                    <h2 data-uuid="887b402d09334fe9a643c7101fdd62c7">Zachary Taylor: New Possibilities</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="4b278ac393a3454488afd7f2a00e56d4">General Taylor’s successful military campaigns in the War of 1812 and the recent Mexican-American War made him a household name and opened new political possibilities.</p>
                </div>
